The project is implemented using ServiceNow Import Sets and Transform Maps.

Steps:

Upload Excel file into Import Set
Create staging table for temporary data storage
Configure Transform Map to map fields to target table
Use Dot Walking for relationship mapping between tables
Add script to map related records (e.g., manager)
Execute transform to move data into target table

Script used:

var mgr = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
mgr.addQuery('email', source.u_manager_email);
mgr.query();
if (mgr.next()) {
    target.manager = mgr.sys_id;
}
